Package: mmdh
Version: 0.1-1
Date: 2026-02-19
Type: Package
Title: Helper Functions for MoSPI Microdata
Authors@R: person("Deepayan", "Sarkar", role = c("aut", "cre"),
	          email = "deepayan.sarkar@r-project.org",
	          comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4107-1553"))
Description: The Ministry of Statistics and Programme Implementation
	     (MoSPI), Government of India, releases anonymized
	     microdata for various sample surveys it conducts. The
	     public-use data are available from the ministry website
	     in various formats, but cannot be redistributed because
	     individual registration is required before the data can
	     be used. This package provides a collection of functions
	     and metadata that may be useful in preprocessing the data
	     after it has been downloaded.
LazyData: yes
